Dialogue: 1,0:23:47.78,0:23:50.57,JP PRE A-OTF Shin Go Pr6N B,,0,0,0,,{\fsp0}僕たちは「ヘヴンスレイブ」に泥を塗ったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.57,0:23:52.49,JP PRE A-OTF Shin Go Pr6N B,,0,0,0,,「アンフィスバエナ」に何の用
Dialogue: 1,0:23:52.49,0:23:54.53,JP PRE A-OTF Shin Go Pr6N B,,0,0,0,,折原臨也から目を離すな
Dialogue: 1,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.28,JP PRE A-OTF Shin Go Pr6N B,,0,0,0,,雲井さんはお怒りだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:56.28,0:23:59.33,JP PRE A-OTF Shin Go Pr6N B,,0,0,0,,次回「口に蜜、心に針」
